t: Elk Group International Rebrands as Elk Home
s: January 5, 2021 - ELK Group International (EGI) is now Elk Home, a spokesperson for the company announced this week. The new name, Elk Home, is part of a larger rebranding effort that represents months of strategic planning and consolidates EGI and its subsidiaries into one brand.
